      "content": "hey i am looking at my mortgage statement from wells fargo and im kinda confused. i have a 30 year fixed loan for $450,000 at a 6.5% interest rate. can u show me how the payments change over time? like how much of my monthly payment is actually going to the principal vs the interest in year 5 compared to year 25? i want to see the difference.",
